, next to the guest’s smart beige cap, there remained a crumpled piece of soft paper: the wrappings of liberated roses. He rummaged in his father’s overcoat, penetrating with squeamish fingers into the insensate world of a strange pocket, but did not find there the spare pack he had hoped to obtain, knowing as he did his father’s heavyish providence. Nothing to be done, I must go to him.

